The paper proposes a method for optimization using estimation of distribution algorithms, which are commonly used in the field of neural networks (cs.NE) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses fitness estimation and niche preservation, which are topics related to machine learning (cs.LG) and data structures (cs.DS). Finally, the paper discusses problem decomposition and sub-structure identification, which are topics related to software engineering (cs.SE).
